<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.113898.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Living habit of specimens of three Macrobrachium species A, B M. lanchesteri from Bang Khiat, Singhanakhon, Songkhla, Thailand C, D M. rostrolevatus sp. nov. from Bueng Khong Long, Bueng Kan, Thailand E M. panhai sp. nov. from Sri Nakarin Dam, Tha Kradan, Si Sawat, Kanchanaburi, Thailand. Scale bars: 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/974855" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.113898.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Morphological characteristics of Macrobrachium lanchesteri (A female topotype MUMNH MP 00218 B-H female topotype MUMNH MP 00216.1) A lateral view B carapace C epistome D second pereiopod E teeth between fingers F third pereiopod G uropod and H movable spine at uropodal diaeresis. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/974856" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

